event.description:
We regularly host a variety of parties, events and functions across all 4 floors of our venue.  In the past 6 months alone we have catered for numerous personal gathering for birthdays, farewells & engagements as well as corporate meetings, dinners, networking drinks and team parties.

We can accommodate parties of 2 - 20 on single tables and have great options for larger parties and exclusive use / private dining 7 days a week.

We take great care of dietary requirements and allergies, catering particularly well for gluten free diets.  Our Set Banquet Menus come in 2 sizes, $65pp and $80pp and each menu has the option of all savoury or to include a sweet course.

We have flexible spaces and a flexible attitude so give us a call on 03 9663 6363 to speak with one of our lovely team members about your next event!
event.disclaimer: Restaurants are solely responsible for the service; availability and quality of the events including all or any cancellations/ modifications/ complaints.
event.title: Events & Functions
